#40001
Name:	Combat Training - Non-Ballistic
Desc:$
   All along the walls are mounted weapons, some artifacts of ancient elven
civilizations lost eons ago, some historic remnants of feudal Japan, such as
ancient katanas, sais, no-dachi, and so forth.  A suit of early Renaissance
field plate stands next to a chainmail samurai armor suit, both worn by
statues depicting ages old warriors.  The hall continues to the north and to
the east, where you see numerous types of training equipment, and target
practice dummies. 
~
