#40002
Name:	Combat Training - Ballistic
Desc:$
   Surrounding you are target dummies set up for neophyte gunners, pockmarked
with bullet marks of all calibres, from hold-out to assault cannon and mortar
rounds.  How these dummies still stand is a mystery.  Practice weapons are
lined up on racks, for the use of the neophytic guild, as well as rubber
practice rounds.  Looks like that mystery is solved. 
~
