#40003
Name:	Drivers' Education
Desc:$
   Along a wall are a myriad of simulators for vehicles, ranging from
everything from a scooter to a panzer.  A few of them are marked "Out Of
Order", but the most commonly used ones are functional.  On the other end of
this garage like area are torn up and rebuilt automobiles with students
learning how to upgrade and repair just about anything with an engine.  An
arena is erected on the northern end of the room for practicing the use of
remote control devices. 
~
