Name:	Magical Training
Desc:$
   On the north wall, you see an array of hermetic formulae in geometric
patterns, with students studying them, glossing over their symbolic meanings,
and how they relate to the structure of astral space.  On the south wall are
several totem poles, and masks, for each of the major totems common to North
America. 
~
