#40005
Name:	Lingustics School
Desc:$
   You enter a large library, stuffed full of books on languages of every kind
imaginable, from Japanese and Chinese to Sperethiel and even Sioux. There are
seats and long tables set up with simsense terminals for accelerated learning
systems, and tutors on call to help one through the understanding of the
intricacies of the languages.  On the walls are various program posters that
say words such as "Welcome" in fifty ore more languages. 
~
