#40006
Name:	Adept Ability Training Area
Desc:$
   This room is laid out like a small dojo, with mats laid out at even
intervals, and people practicing martial arts stances.  What makes it a little
different are some of the things people are practicing on, such as breaking
iron bars with their fists, smashing through meter thick pieces of concrete,
and the like.  Upon the walls are pictures of black belt champion physical
adepts of several traditions who have trained in this very room. 
~
