#40008
Name:	Runner Skills Training
Desc:$
   This training station is circular shaped, and along the walls are
bookshelves, with titles ranging from Advanced Perl by O'Reilly Books to The
Art of the Ninja. A few simsense rigs are set up for hands-on training for
deckers and virtual schools for stealth and other skills a runner might need.
A small electronics shop sits on one end of the room, with various chips,
circuit boards, and breadboard setups for training people with electronics. 
~
